name: Dean Fujioka
description: {{Nihongo|'''Tatsuo Fujioka'''|藤岡 竜雄|Fujioka Tatsuo|born August 19, 1980}}, better known as {{Nihongo|'''Dean Fujioka'''|ディーン・フジオカ|Dīn Fujioka|stylized as '''DEAN FUJIOKA'''}} is a Japanese actor, voice actor, singer, songwriter, musician, model and film director/producer.
